g the dynamic properties of glassy systems is also\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2009 06:44:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Dec 2009 07:36:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
