. The understanding of such unusual relaxation process is obtained by\nthe introduction of an appropriate kinetic theory based on the Vlasov equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2009 09:52:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2009 20:03:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-03"}
